2001-12-04  mlang  <mlang@users.sf.net>

	* erc.el:
	* (erc-send-current-line): Fixed long outstanding bug. XEmacs users with erc-fill-region on erc-insert-hook knew that one a long time.

	* erc.el: fix order of attack

